⊢         Every teacher. Is. A person.

ro lo mikce cu prenu
⊢ RULE    ∀x. doctor(x) → person(x)
⊢         Every doctor. Is. A person.

ro lo flaselcu'u cu prenu
⊢ RULE    ∀x. lawyer(x) → person(x)
⊢         Every lawyer. Is. A person.


