⊢ RULE    ∀x. milk(x) → food(x)
⊢         All milk. Is. Food.

ro lo grute cu cidja
⊢ RULE    ∀x. fruit(x) → food(x)
⊢         All fruit. Is. Food.

ro lo nanba cu cidja
⊢ RULE    ∀x. bread(x) → food(x)
⊢         All bread. Is. Food.

