⊢ RULE    ∀x. meat(x) → food(x)
⊢         All meat. Is. Food.


── SUBSTANCES ────────────────────────────────────────

ro lo djacu cu litki
⊢ RULE    ∀x. water(x) → liquid(x)
⊢         All water. Is. Liquid.

ro lo ladru cu litki
⊢ RULE    ∀x. milk(x) → liquid(x)
⊢         All milk. Is. Liquid.


── LIGHT SOURCES ─────────────────────────────────────

ro lo solri cu gusni
⊢ RULE    ∀x. sun(x) → luminous(x)
⊢         The sun. Is. Luminous.

ro lo fagri cu gusni
⊢ RULE    ∀x. fire(x) → luminous(x)
⊢         All fire. Is. Luminous.


── PROFESSIONAL PURPOSE ──────────────────────────────

ro lo ctuca cu se djica lo nu tadni
⊢ RULE    ∀x. teacher(x) → desires(x, ∃e. learning(e))
⊢         Every teacher. Desires. Learning. That is their purpose.

ro lo mikce cu se djica lo nu kanro
⊢ RULE    ∀x. doctor(x) → desires(x, ∃e. health(e))
⊢         Every doctor. Desires. Health. That is their purpose.

ro lo flaselcu'u cu se djica lo nu javni
⊢ RULE    ∀x. lawyer(x) → desires(x, ∃e. rules(e))
⊢         Every lawyer. Desires. Rules. That is their purpose.


── COMMON SENSE ──────────────────────────────────────

ro lo barda danlu cu sutra
⊢ RULE    ∀x. big-animal(x) → fast(x)
⊢         Every big animal. Is. Fast. Common sense heuristic.

ro lo cmalu danlu cu masno
⊢ RULE    ∀x. small-animal(x) → slow(x)
⊢         Every small animal. Is. Slow. Common sense heuristic.


── THE FIREWALL AXIOMS ───────────────────────────────

ro lo xanri cu na birti
⊢ AXIOM   ∀x. imaginary(x) → ¬certain(x)
⊢         Nothing imaginary. Is. Certain. This is non-negotiable.

ro lo birti cu na xanri
⊢ AXIOM   ∀x. certain(x) → ¬imaginary(x)
⊢         Nothing certain. Is. Imaginary. The converse holds.

ro lo logji birti cu se nibli
⊢ AXIOM   ∀x. logical-certainty(x) → derived(x)
⊢         Every logical certainty. Is. Derived. No exceptions. No approximations.


── LAW AND OBLIGATION ────────────────────────────────

ro lo flalu cu javni
⊢ RULE    ∀x. law(x) → rule(x)
⊢         Every law. Is. A rule.

ro lo javni cu se bilga
⊢ RULE    ∀x. rule(x) → obligatory(x)
⊢         Every rule. Creates. Obligation.

ro lo se bilga cu se curmi na se fanta
⊢ RULE    ∀x. obligatory(x) → permitted(x) ∧ ¬blocked(x)
⊢         Obligations. Are. Permitted. And cannot be blocked.


── DATA SOVEREIGNTY ──────────────────────────────────

ro lo datni cu se ponse
⊢ RULE    ∀x. data(x) → owned(x)
⊢         All data. Has. An owner.

ro lo se ponse datni cu se kurji
⊢ RULE    ∀x. owned-data(x) → protected(x)
⊢         All owned data. Requires. Protection.

ro lo se kurji datni cu se fanta lo na se curmi
⊢ RULE    ∀x. protected-data(x) → blocked(x, ¬permitted)
⊢         Protected data. Blocks. The unauthorised. No one passes without permission.


── THE DECLARATION ───────────────────────────────────

lo xanri fanta bitmu cu se zbasu fi lo logji
⊢ GROUND  hallucination-firewall BUILT-FROM logic
⊢         The hallucination firewall. Is built. From logic. Nothing else.

lo xanri fanta bitmu cu birti ciste
⊢ GROUND  hallucination-firewall ∈ certainty-system
⊢         The hallucination firewall. Is. A certainty system.

lo xanri fanta bitmu cu na xanri ciste
⊢ GROUND  hallucination-firewall ∈ ¬imaginary-system
⊢         The hallucination firewall. Is not. An imaginary system. End of file.

